<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />For Yahweh will not forsake his people</para>

<para style="q1">or abandon his inheritance.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />For judgment will again be righteous;</para>

<para style="q1">and all the upright in heart will follow it.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="16" style="v" />Who will rise up to defend me against the evildoers?</para>

<para style="q1">Who will stand up for me against the wicked?</para>
